  <title>Mathematica Terminology</title>
  <p>
    As we
    saw in <xref ref="SECTIONexponential-growth"></xref>
    <m>f(x)=\left(\frac12\right)^x</m> is said to <q>decay exponentially.</q>
  </p>
</aside>

